product_name: Mosquito Deleto Bug Control Spray & Repellent (2-Pack)
description:
More coverage, more savings, more mosquito-free memories

Enjoy a full season outdoor living with our powerful, pet-safe* mosquito killer spray duo.

Why choose the 2-pack? Because mosquitoes don't take vacations! Stock up on our botanical blend of lemongrass and cedar oils to maintain protection all season long. Perfect for larger yards or creating multiple mosquito-free zones, two bottles mean you're always ready for the next application—plus you save 10% on top of free shipping.

Sunday creates effective pest control solutions that harness the power of plants to protect your outdoor living spaces.

PRODUCT FEATURES/BENEFITS

sections.faq:
How often should I apply it?
Apply every 14 days in regions with higher precipitation, or every 28 days for drier areas.
Should I spray my entire lawn?
Rather than covering the entire lawn, designate a “protected zone” in the area where you spend the most time. Spray this zone regularly.
How do I get the best results?
Apply twice within the first 7 days to boost your new pest barrier. After that, stick to your regular schedule to maintain your protected zone, and consider additional bumper applications after rainy weather (or ahead of hosting your annual BBQ or lawn game night!).
How many square feet does one bottle cover?
Up to 5,000 sq. ft.
Should I use Mosquito Deleto before or after Sunday nutrients?
You can apply either one first—the order is totally up to you! Regardless, you’ll want to wait 24 hours between those applications to avoid washing out or diluting either formula.
Are there any US states or territories where Mosquito Deleto is not approved for use?
Mosquito Deleto is not yet approved for use in the following states and territories: DC, ID, IN, MD, ME, MS, MT.
